Reasoning: The paper discusses quantum computing and quantum automata, which are topics related to theoretical computer science. Specifically, the paper focuses on quantum finite automata and their various models, as well as related topics such as interactive proof systems, quantum communication complexity, and query complexity. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.ET (Emerging Technologies), which covers new and emerging areas of computer science research. Other likely sub-categories include cs.CC (Computational Complexity), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science), and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
